Calcium-activated potassium channel slowpoke (Maxi K channel) (MaxiK)
(BK channel) (dSlo).
"A component of calcium-activated potassium channels encoded by the
Drosophila slo locus.";
"Calcium-activated potassium channels expressed from cloned
complementary DNAs.";
"The genome sequence of Drosophila melanogaster.";
"Annotation of the Drosophila melanogaster euchromatic genome: a
systematic review.";
