    Q8IPH9:Slob; NbExp=1; IntAct=EBI-426805, EBI-142379;
    Q8IPH9-1:Slob; NbExp=1; IntAct=EBI-426805, EBI-424896;
    P00528:Src64B; NbExp=3; IntAct=EBI-426805, EBI-87092;
-!- SUBCELLULAR LOCATION: Membrane; multi-pass membrane protein
    (Probable).
